notesStmt.note: Manuscript book of lectures given by William Cullen and used by Benjamin Rush and his son, James. Volume 4 of 4.

Benjamin Rush studied medicine under William Cullen, and began teaching at the University of Pennsylvania in 1769. He became a professor of medical theory and clinical practice in 1791. He died in 1813.
